</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_165_r2l3"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie daʒ Jm beẏ Prünne etwieuil <del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſein<ex>er</ex></expan></del> hab mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_165_r2l4"><expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> pferd vnd
                                <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> ſein hab
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſeẏ <expan>woꝛde<ex>n</ex></expan> /
                                <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>
</ab>
<ab facs="#facs_165_r2l5">daʒ Jr durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
                        hilff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darcʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_165_r2l6">tun wöllet / ob dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
                        ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
