</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_165" id="81r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Hyniko, hauptman czu Prünne </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> her Hyniko, uns hat fürgelegt Laurencz
                                <expan>Groland<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, wie daz im bey Prünne etwievil hab mit
                                <expan>name<ex>n</ex></expan> pferd und
                            <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> sein hab <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sey <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>. <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir
                        durch <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> hilff und <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan>
                        darczu tun wöllet, ob dem <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, dieselb sein habe widerwerde
                        <add>möht</add>. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Der stat czu Prunne <expan>si<ex>mi</ex>l<ex>ite</ex>r</expan>.</ab>
